author: @hey608
text:
For the people who want to understand why the new unit is named NCT WISH. In the video of MAMA 2020 explain it.

"The moment when the wave of dreams meet the wave of reality, Awakening from a dream means your wish becomes reality".

That is why NCT WISH has the teaser of AESPA.  It's to show that now all nct members are awake in the real world living their wishes.

There was a reason for the name and the teaser (AESPA-My World), so people need to stop complaining without knowing.
